According to the documentation, you need to assign the result of tf.InteractiveSession to a variable:
https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/r0.11/api_docs/python/client.html#InteractiveSession

That being said, the behavior seems to be different between 0.10 and nightly build, so this may be working differently now. Could you try it in the nightly build?

body:
According to the documentation, you need to assign the result of `tf.InteractiveSession` to a variable:
https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/r0.11/api_docs/python/client.html#InteractiveSession

That being said, the behavior seems to be different between 0.10 and nightly build, so this may be working differently now. Could you try it in the nightly build?
